Package ut.twente.notebridge.model

Class BaseEntity

java.lang.Object
ut.twente.notebridge.model.BaseEntity
Direct Known Subclasses:
BaseUser, Comment, Feedback, Message, MessageHistory, Post
public class BaseEntity extends Object
This class represents a base entity in the application. Since id, createDate, lastUpdate are common fields in all entities, they are defined here Other entity classes extend this class
